{"type": "article", "id": 27499, "title": "可以切换香味的香薰机", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115736gEkoVIHGr7iySQOJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>在家休息时，打开香薰机已经成为不少人的选择。免去清洗和加水的烦恼，日本设计师 Fumie Shibata 为品牌 @aroma 设计了一款可以随时切换香味的压电式香薰机 <a href=\"http://www.at-aroma.com/duo/\">duo</a>，香味的扩散范围最大可以达到 70 平方米。通过上端的按钮可以对 duo 进行定时或者是切换香味，在设定的时间内机器就会自动运行。这是它的<a href=\"http://store.at-aroma.com/products/detail.php?product_id=589\">购买链接</a>，售价为 54000 日元。配套的 @aroma 香油则需要额外购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021157341jydovbF4zuQm7lR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115735l1SkpJxYEBncQIZw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115735tfBYzM12onrJLdl6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}